coexist and contribute. Investing in gender equality in science is not merely a matter of fairness; it's an investment in innovation, progress, and a brighter future for all. This requires a collective effort from educators, policymakers, institutions, and individuals alike, all working in harmony towards a world where scientific exploration knows no gender boundaries.",
